"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"大家好，我是mer君，今天搞一个听名字就很像跨链的项目\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fzmb-htWirpErnBHhqy4E.png?height=487&width=598)\\n\\n推荐理由：\\n\\n1\\\\.侧链和跨链一直是我觉得必埋伏的板块之一，所以没有理由，必须冲\\n\\n2\\\\.明确空投激励\\n\\n————————————首先看看官方介绍————————————\\n\\n[https://medium.com/@bridgenetwork/bridge-network-testnet-is-live-with-its-airdrop-program-6ad3ed5cba09#id_token=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImNhMDA2MjBjNWFhN2JlOGNkMDNhNmYzYzY4NDA2ZTQ1ZTkzYjNjYWIiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ..PmDWdbmnBBs6VfZRi_eIWYXCPH-NsZWKy-28QpROWXkBKZ0izYavg0crC2xs5U5Sj8xE_LNO91zcixkds5J0Pzr4mdovFv_M9kLVzor7-o0W_pfh5L575hazss9QjMGmE2jGjks0ky9Qy50Yne__Nt4J3zg2RS35SNGmS3_wrGW2ZkTGsqgsQ6c1Q6j_1L7qM2W1a-6VsFfoUp6M_Ve_YjDuJfezHwBuwkP1W--xXPsHn-0SfgsJyNtkwQnPekLjnbVaKsV3W-ZvSS0tX80taZ6yGp-iWIqlspf-dL-G-PiIqHLVJCJcRG6n3IropzqO9Earh_r6gcUlThRIM9UbPA](https://medium.com/@bridgenetwork/bridge-network-testnet-is-live-with-its-airdrop-program-6ad3ed5cba09#id_token=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImNhMDA2MjBjNWFhN2JlOGNkMDNhNmYzYzY4NDA2ZTQ1ZTkzYjNjYWIiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ..PmDWdbmnBBs6VfZRi_eIWYXCPH-NsZWKy-28QpROWXkBKZ0izYavg0crC2xs5U5Sj8xE_LNO91zcixkds5J0Pzr4mdovFv_M9kLVzor7-o0W_pfh5L575hazss9QjMGmE2jGjks0ky9Qy50Yne__Nt4J3zg2RS35SNGmS3_wrGW2ZkTGsqgsQ6c1Q6j_1L7qM2W1a-6VsFfoUp6M_Ve_YjDuJfezHwBuwkP1W--xXPsHn-0SfgsJyNtkwQnPekLjnbVaKsV3W-ZvSS0tX80taZ6yGp-iWIqlspf-dL-G-PiIqHLVJCJcRG6n3IropzqO9Earh_r6gcUlThRIM9UbPA)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/RsOk7Rb0jQSMPMZ1dXasl.png?height=642&width=837)\\n\\n时间截止到22号，还有时间，快冲\\n\\n——————————————————————————————————\\n\\n我们直接开始：\\n\\n1\\\\.领水\\n\\n[https://www.bridgenetwork.com/testnetguide](https://www.bridgenetwork.com/testnetguide)\\n\\n进入官网\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4lG7cUt3HTUUaNr7fkipg.png?height=706&width=833)\\n\\n下拉一下，找到领水的地方分别把测试币领了，本文以ETH到MATIC的跨链为解释说明\\n\\n————————以下内容针对纯新手——————————\\n\\n（1）领ETH的水\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jlYjsYIZqDP2AUMlsFEtp.png?height=664&width=783)\\n\\n点开上面图片提及get $ETH，跳转到下图界面\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/g5PqdQoyPcV3Wue51QC9m.png?height=608&width=1307)\\n\\n点击如图的“tweet”位置\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8x4Moo9nDC7I_jFsUv1KL.png?height=402&width=722)\\n\\n自动跳转到发推特的界面，然后把如图0X……0的地方换成你的钱包地址，发推\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QhGFxSEB-14bFYM9Y9rsc.png?height=655&width=1001)\\n\\n回到推特的个人资料界面，找到刚才发的推特，点击分享\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/r4LsVsat1bOEAgxKqIiMm.png?height=443&width=742)\\n\\n复制此条推文的链接\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6BoIhQVxeoV0WmZrNjVRI.png?height=501&width=1321)\\n\\n回到之前的领水界面，把推特链接粘贴进去，点击Give me ETH\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nQ5hv8DiqHD0nwqtL7pjx.png?height=176&width=278)\\n\\n直接选18.75那个就行\\n\\n（2）领MATIC的测试币\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Wg62cSDSStqBERM5Btu_a.png?height=593&width=796)\\n\\n点击如图\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/KEyUtfim79P8PbHZTgaN8.png?height=585&width=719)\\n\\n粘贴你的钱包地址，submit后确认即可\\n\\n————————————————————————————————————\\n\\n2\\\\.测试\\n\\n[https://testnet.bridgenetwork.com/](https://testnet.bridgenetwork.com/)\\n\\n进入测试官网界面\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_b1DXQ9bzZO3sObEqwCVO.png?height=139&width=359)\\n\\n先将小狐狸切换到rinkeby测试网络\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/gy8jek0JwIZetubmy4CaZ.png?height=570&width=1532)\\n\\n右上角链接钱包\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jzolasjgPkGUbhB9xYzne.png?height=862&width=1022)\\n\\n如图操作，就是基本的跨链操作，选择好转出网络和接收网络，填入跨链数量，选择接收地址\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QXHtjs5PX87ViWj2rbvIK.png?height=370&width=847)\\n\\n确认即可\\n\\n同理，我们做一遍MATIC跨到ETH，有时间的做下别的链条，总之就各种跨\\n\\n3\\\\.关注推特加入电报\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xu7-BcAHAd56rS4afPM5-.png?height=323&width=548)\\n\\n关注和加入，后面填表要用\\n\\n4\\\\.填表\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pKHYYjz7Ci6YdG12KZcQL.png?height=421&width=791)\\n\\n我们继续下拉到这里，点它\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/RpPR5bhlxlHnox7nRL-NV.png?height=923&width=900)\\n\\n按图填写完事\\n\\n以上。\",\"timestamp\":1642606249,\"title\":\"BridgeNetwork(rinkeby/……)\"},\"digest\":\"nBLYTspukbuB4D1OsuyM38cbBIuiboGQVt_ZesXGJLU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7F51c8447eE363d7bE2705163CC81f524685A008\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2EEIIHXF6mk83dYFwguf_bd8Hkho-hWHb2HffWktQNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"SonPpIOVvnZ9ssKsgV2GQM-CP32qAD8pNVb4TUsEeP4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SuTJHvz1k8f-pr6xe8ECYmDbK0WPDP5O12JpRui1y6yyhq0WCo0jo_OL34DR5fjpJJeUQ1eNlc2ENqMpkNMw0g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x803ce80aac0dc83930c8a1905d0cfd210c6fcb8d610acce3821f708b8a2538356097232d82b7ccd2946b82889adc536f1ff703cf600dd33f266b273a7d2d6ef51c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2EEIIHXF6mk83dYFwguf_bd8Hkho-hWHb2HffWktQNc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"SonPpIOVvnZ9ssKsgV2GQM-CP32qAD8pNVb4TUsEeP4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"R9b76qriV-L1JOK_muGnhzcvVZP4B9DnB5gdmHMzeuo\"}"